# DESIGN SYSTEM
- minimalist concept
- label instead of icon for signaling term

# SYSTEM DESIGN
- modular approach to enforce single responsibility
- limit nested folder into max 3 depth
- vanilla react
- bundled using webpack

# NAMING CONVENTIONS
- directory: flatcase
- file: PascalCase
- label: PascalCase (except styled components theme instance)
- leading character: capital with underscore next to it before the label
  P_ => Pages
  C_ => Components
  S_ => Styles
  T_ => Statics
  U_ => Utils
